Next Event: January 25, 2016
'Watson + Robots = Cognitive IoT'
Abstract: Ever wondered how to build a robot that talks to you? Thanks to Watson and the emergence of cheap, hackable computer boards it's never been easier to do. During this session we'll give a few best practices and a high level intro to Watson in the IoT space.


